---
<div class="newsletter-box">
	<div class="newsletter-content">
		<h3>¿Te fascina el futuro?</h3>
		<p>Únete a +5,000 mentes curiosas y recibe cada semana los descubrimientos más impactantes de Nature y Science directamente en tu bandeja de entrada.</p>
		<form class="newsletter-form" onsubmit="return false;">
			<input type="email" placeholder="Tu mejor email..." required />
			<button type="submit">Suscribirme Gratis</button>
		</form>
		<div class="alternative-channels" style="margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px;">
			<a href="#" class="whatsapp-btn" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #25D366; color: white; padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem;">
				<span>🟢</span> Únete al Canal de WhatsApp
			</a>
		</div>
		<span class="spam-free" style="display: block; margin-top: 1rem;">🔒 Sin spam. Solo ciencia de alta autoridad.</span>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	.newsletter-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0070f3 0%, #00c6ff 100%);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
		color: white;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 112, 243, 0.2);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
	:global([data-theme='dark']) .newsletter-box {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #004a99 0%, #0070f3 100%);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}
	.newsletter-content h3 {
		color: white;
		margin-top: 0;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.newsletter-content p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
		color: white;
	}
	.newsletter-form {
		display: flex;
		gap: 10px;
		max-width: 500px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
	}
	.newsletter-form input {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
		font-size: 1rem;
		outline: none;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		color: #333;
	}
	:global([data-theme='dark']) .newsletter-form input {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: white;
		border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
	}
	:global([data-theme='dark']) .newsletter-form input::placeholder {
		color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
	}
	.newsletter-form button {
		background: #000;
		color: white;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
	}
	:global([data-theme='dark']) .newsletter-form button {
		background: #ffffff;
		color: #000;
	}
	.newsletter-form button:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}
	.spam-free {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		opacity: 0.7;
		font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
	}
	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.newsletter-form { flex-direction: column; }
	}
</style>
